thread.title: Missing teen may have flown to Cancun with 45-year-old man

title: Missing teen may have flown to Cancun with 45-year-old man
text:
Missing teen may have flown to Cancun with 45-year-old man Friday, March 16, 2018 - 01:42 
Police say a 16-year-old Pennsylvania teen, who went missing after she was signed out of school by a 45-year-old man, may have flown to Cancun with him. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
